title: LSAT Tests and ALL Explanations, plus Bibles
description:
There are 37 tests in total. Includes prep tests 7, 9-16, and 18-45.

Also includes explanations for ALL tests 1-56 straight from KAPLAN.

Finally, logic games and logic reasoning bibles are included.

This is my collection from various downloads plus a personal contribution of the test explanations. If anyone has any of the missing tests (1-6, 8, 17, 46-present) or the lsat proctor dvd, please upload or let me know where to find it. Thanks, and good luck studying!

Included: 

"10 Actual, Official LSAT Preptests"

"10 More Actual, Official LSAT Preptests"

"The Next 10 Actual, Official LSAT Preptests"

Tests 39-45

PowerScore's LSAT Logic Games Bible

PowerScore's LSAT Logic Reasoning Bible

Kaplan Test Explanations, 1-56
